{"tid":1956841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"掛國旗區旗特區政府機構明日下半旗向疫情逝世同胞致哀","createTime":"2020-04-03T12:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T16:24:18.000Z","uid":225818,"like":7,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8054f2408c04d5ca7ff7c0e4ebef86a14645213f","tid":1956841,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"國務院早前宣布，明日為新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情中，逝世同胞舉行悼念儀式，包括舉行全國哀悼活動、停止公共娛樂活動，以及全國及駐外使領館，下半旗致哀。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府表示，明日懸掛國旗及區旗的政府機構亦會下半旗致哀，行政長官早上10時與立法會主席、行政會議成員及司局長，將會在行政長官辦公室默哀3分鐘。<br />\n<br />\nsource RTHK<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518744-20200403.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518744-20200403.htm&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=0d640577\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518744-20200403.htm&h=ab362f86\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518744-20200403.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n關香港人咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？致咩哀？<br />\n預知聽朝10點心情會好好<br />\n雖然唔係咩特別日子<br />\n不過就好想慶祝<br />\n大家有咩提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d17849c78af9407eb04eb69c60b938f7b70ca10","tid":1956841,"uid":92448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:45:05.000Z","msg":"死左曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9de0eee45aba3eed202ba23dfc62e97681ff2ca","tid":1956841,"uid":2654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"全民慶祝日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720d0ae94e8b61ef73b9d0c88e04c207166a7b3f","tid":1956841,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"咁快有mon post曱甴入黎負皮<img src=\"